resources.string: Hello, this is a new Netology! Once upon a time, Netology began with intensive courses in online marketing. Then there were courses in design, development, analytics and management. We grow by ourselves and help students grow: from beginners to confident professionals. But the most important thing remains with us: we believe that everyone already has the power to want more, aim higher, and run faster. Our mission is to help us embark on the path of growth and begin the chain of change http://netolo.gy/fyb
Netology. University of the Internet Professions of the Future
